After the long journey, I'm extremely happy to share that my green card application has been approved !!! 🥹

It was such a big excitement. I couldn't be more thankful to my wife @pasinee__p for all your help and support throughout the process. I can't wait to spend my life with you ☺️

I would like to thank you to all photo editors, photo producers, creative directors and everyone in this industry who support me in my career these past years. I really came to New York with a dream but you all made it happen to me. I also want to thank you to all friends who encourage me along the way. Without you all I wouldn't have come this far ❤️

Thank you again for having me here. Thank you for all your support. I'm very happy and super ready to keep my journey going with you all ❤️

So proud to say I volunteer to be one of the photographers to shoot @sendchinatownlove cookbook (and cover) !

Back in 2020 when covid hit the city, I followed SCL for their work in helping local restaurant businesses in Chinatown. Last year the team reached out to me asking for my help to photograph these restaurants for the community. It's such a great feeling to know that my photography skill can help the community in some ways 😊

Made Here is more than a cookbook, and it's about more than just making food — it's about making a home, making a life, and making it in New York City. Check out @sendchinatownlove to pre-order the book.

Thank you for SCL team for having me on this project 🙏 @natbelkov @elainekmao @smugluord @tuyenktran and so many people on SCL team that I haven't had a chance to work with. Also sending love to my fellow photographers 😘 @janicekaramchung @cindytrinh.photo @joykimjoy @willstevens

Love you all ❤️

Just got a chance to share this campaign I worked with Universal studios @unistudios over the last year with the support from @mythology @goldieproductionsla @goldteethandco . We worked with Universal Destinations & Experiences to create this campaign!!!

"We used real people, real rides, real screams and real feelings to show the world that Universal is the place for unbridled, uncalculated, real insanity of the best kind."

Thank you so much for all the support through out the campaign. It has been such a fun challenge and experience working on this shoot. So happy to see them in real life 😊

2023 ❤️

This year would have never been so great without all the amazing people I got to work with. Thank you to all of you who made my life and my dream in NYC become true everyday. Coming from a place where my work and my words have never been valued, I am forever grateful for all the support I got here. Thank you for all your trust in me. I'm looking forward to going along my journey in the upcoming years with you all.

Thank you again ❤️

🌟Personal News 🌟

Happy new year. Happy new chapter of life.
My green card has finally arrived !!! 🎉🎉🎉

After all the hard work in these past years, I finally am a permanent resident in the US!!! Coming from an industry with poor support for women professional photographer, I'm forever grateful for all the opportunities given to me here to make this happen.

Thank you to everyone who helped me through the process. It has been a long journey. I couldn't make it without all the support from the photo community here. Thank you for seeing my work, listening to my voice, supporting my career. I really appreciate it ❤️🙏

Since I got a lot of support from the industry, I want to support young professionals as much as I can. I'm still thinking of myself at an early stage in my career but hopefully I can help somehow. I will keep creating work and trying my best as usual.

Thank you again for all the support. Couldn't ask for a greater start of 2024.

Let's celebrate!!! 🥳🥳🥳
